snippet.title: Holy Potatoes! We're in Space?! Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore a vegetabulous Universe with Cassie and Fay in their journey to rescue their grandfather, Jiji! Defeat your enemies in strategic turn-based combat, manage your very own spaceship, and explore dozens of procedurally generated planets, stars and galaxies! 

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/505730/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/holypotatogame/

http://www.day-lightstudios.com
http://www.holypotatoesgame.com
http://www.daedalic.com
